<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="page-glow page-glow--left"></view>
  <view class="page-glow page-glow--right"></view>

  <view class="stack" wx:if="{{previewAdmin}}">
    <view class="hero-panel">
      <view class="hero-kicker">Admin Only</view>
      <view class="hero-title">管理员控制台</view>
      <view class="hero-copy">
        这里负责 VIP 升级、延长天数、强制下线和删帖。用户端不应开放这些能力。
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="card-panel">
      <view class="section-head">
        <view class="section-title">VIP 规则</view>
        <button class="button-mini" bindtap="refreshPosts">刷新列表</button>
      </view>
      <view class="helper-text" style="margin-top: 16rpx;">
        管理员可将任意帖子升级为 VIP，最多 3 张图，最长 360 天。正式环境中，图片应由管理员在微信内上传后写入云存储文件 ID。
      </view>
      <view class="helper-text" style="margin-top: 10rpx;">{{adminHint}}</view>
      <view class="helper-text" style="margin-top: 10rpx;">当前可管理帖子：{{postCount}} 条</view>
    </view>

    <view class="empty-state" wx:if="{{!posts.length}}">
      当前还没有可管理的帖子。
      先从“发帖子”发布一条信息，或者下拉刷新 / 点击上方刷新列表后再回来。
    </view>

    <view class="field-list" wx:else>
      <view class="post-card" wx:for="{{posts}}" wx:key="id">
        <view class="post-head">
          <view>
            <view class="post-title">{{item.title}}</view>
            <view class="post-meta" style="margin-top: 10rpx;">{{item.categoryLabel}} / {{item.intentLabel}} / {{item.statusLabel}}</view>
          </view>
          <view class="tag {{item.tier === 'vip' ? 'tag--warm' : ''}}">
            {{item.tier === "vip" ? "VIP" : "普通"}}
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="field-list">
          <view class="helper-text">{{item.mediaModerationLabelText}}</view>

          <view>
            <text class="field-label">输入 VIP 展示天数</text>
            <input
              class="field-input"
              placeholder="1-360"
              data-id="{{item.id}}"
              bindinput="onDaysInput"
              value="{{customDaysById[item.id]}}"
            />
          </view>

          <view>
            <text class="field-label">管理员代上传图片</text>
            <view class="button-row">
              <button class="button-secondary" bindtap="chooseImages" data-id="{{item.id}}">选择图片</button>
            </view>
            <view class="helper-text">VIP 帖最多 3 张图。若不重新选择，则沿用原图片。</view>
            <view class="field-list" style="margin-top: 16rpx;" wx:if="{{localImagesById[item.id] && localImagesById[item.id].length}}">
              <view class="post-card" wx:for="{{localImagesById[item.id]}}" wx:for-item="imagePath" wx:key="*this">
                <image src="{{imagePath}}" mode="aspectFill" class="cover-block" lazy-load="true"></image>
                <button class="button-danger" bindtap="removeImage" data-id="{{item.id}}" data-index="{{index}}">移除</button>
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>

          <view class="button-row">
            <button class="button-primary" bindtap="applyVipUpdate" data-id="{{item.id}}">升级 / 续期</button>
            <button class="button-secondary" bindtap="forceExpire" data-id="{{item.id}}">强制下线</button>
            <button class="button-danger" bindtap="deletePost" data-id="{{item.id}}">删除</button>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:else class="empty-state">
    当前账号不是管理员，或云端白名单尚未配置。
  </view>
</view>
